      "Hip and elbow dysplasia — both OFA-screened in reputable breeding lines. Slow controlled growth as a puppy + lean body weight protects joints.",
      "Lymphedema (hereditary) — congenital lymphatic vessel malformation; presents as swelling of the limbs, sometimes from puppyhood. Distinct from injury-related swelling. Reputable breeders pedigree-test.",
      "Entropion + ectropion — eyelid inversion or eversion; surgical correction prevents corneal damage. Usually addressed by age 2.",
